## Tech Stack

- **Python 3.9+** with PyObjC
- **AppKit / WebKit** â€” Native macOS frameworks
- **WKWebView** â€” Hardware-accelerated web rendering
- **Ollama** â€” Local LLM inference

---

## Troubleshooting

**App doesn't show?**
```bash
python -m overai --check-permissions
```

**Reset settings:**
```bash
rm -rf ~/Library/Application\ Support/OverAI
rm -rf ~/Library/Logs/OverAI
```

